## **NEXT STEPS?**
View the [roadmap](https://www.xivraidplanner.app/docs/roadmap) to see what's comming next. My current priority, which isn't reflected in the roadmap, is to automate and simplify the setup of statics. Right now, the setup process is pretty clunky and takes much longer than it should. These updates should be coming shortly. If anyone is interested in testing the new workflow when it's ready, let me know!

Once I have the workflow polished, and some of the UX improvements added; my plan is to roll this out to an even larger audience. 

Currently, there are 32 statics using this tool, and that's purely through word of mouth. Vercel analytics indicate 354 visitors in the last 7 days. I've been hesitating to post this in Dalamud or The Balance discords, but it's the logical next step if I truly want to share something that could benefit the community as a whole. 

